testCIFSRemoteBackup

public void testCIFSRemoteBackup()
NOTE: This test will work on WINDOWS ONLY This test exists in 5 stages: I) Perform a Factory Reset, wiping any data from previous tests on the machine. II) Add a fetcher named IMAP4, and perform a backup on data fetched. III) Wipe the data, and restore. IV) Add another fetcher named Allison, and perform a backup on fetched data. V) Wipe again, and restore.
